.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-7::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: grey, turquise, purple, blood-red
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: blues, dubstep, metal, soul
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, british, dutch, russian
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, bike, subway, train
 1. the person driving the train is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 2. the person who likes turquise is the dutch##1
 3. the fan of dubstep is between the dutch and the person driving the subway##2
 4. the fan of metal is the person driving the train##1
 5. the russian is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 7. the argentine is the person driving the airplane##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person who likes turquise is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
10. the dutch is the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Color   | purple | turquise | grey  | blood-red  |
| Music-Genre   | blues       | metal   | dubstep | soul    |
| Nationality   | argentine   | dutch   | russian | british |
| Transport     | airplane    | train   | bike    | subway  |

