The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, drama, satire, zombie
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, dahlia, begonia, tulip
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, quad-bike, subway
1. the person watching drama movies is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person driving the car##2
2. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person drinking water##1
3. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
4. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the person drinking lemonade is the person watching zombie movies##1
7. the person drinking water is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
8. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |      3      |   4    |
| Beverage      | lemonade  | water   | iced-tea    | juice  |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie    | drama   | documentary | satire |
| Flower           | iris       | begonia   | dahlia        | tulip  |
| Transport     | quad-bike | jet-ski | car         | subway |

