.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda, sprite
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, reggae, trance, techno
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, hiking, photography, woodworking
4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, rat, turtle
 1. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 2. the owner of the dog is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 4. the fan of salsa is the person drinking lemonade##1
 5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the fan of salsa and the fan of trance##2
 9. the fan of techno is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the fan of salsa and the fan of trance##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
| Beverage   | lemonade    | mirinda    | sprite      | hot-chocolate |
| Music-Genre       | salsa        | techno       | trance       | reggae     |
| Hobby      | photography | filmmaking | woodworking | hiking        |
| Pet        | horse       | turtle     | rat         | dog           |

